fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.data

Interface IType

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IArrayType, IBinaryType, IBooleanType, IDateTimeType, IDateType, IDecimalType, IFloatType, IImageType, IIntegerType, INumberType, IRelationType, ITextType, ITimeType, IUuidType

    public interface IType
    Type of data that may be contained in a specific cell for a specific source.

    Thread safety: implementations are required to be immutable and therefore completely thread-safe.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
    See Also:
    ICell.getType(), IData.getType()
